<Author>ampiBud
<Content>Good hotel for budget travelers Definitely this is a good choice for budget stays in the area. There are no other ones in the neighborhood that could hit the price of this.No breakfast is provided but they have coin laundry, pool, and in my room I had a fully equipped kitchen (microwave, refrigerator, stovetop...) Everything is clean and the staff is helpful. They have complimentary shuttle bus to and from the airport. 
